title: Drink & Write
author: iebagi
pages:
#- Why You Should Never Drink and Write


By iebagi
#- Drinking and Writing do not mix. I once thought so. But they do not. 

Spelling Errors, Grammar Errors, and other types of errors comes when you drink and write. 

I once knew a man, who wrote a book
#- but was drunk. It sold one copy. The one copy was from his mom. His mom hated it. She later died. 


DON'T DRINK AND WRITE.
#- 